/a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bonobo">Bonobo</a> 、Eris Drew、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-radar/dj-python-mas-ambale-review-2648959">DJ Python</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/honey-dijon">Honey Dijon</a>和 Marcel Dettmann 等将在音乐节上表演。</p><p>在英国，最近宣布<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/40-uk-festivals-have-now-been-cancelled-this-summer-with-over-170-disappearing-in-five-years-3758805">今年夏天 40 个英国节日已被取消，新的报告发现过去五年中有 170 多个节日消失</a>。</p><p>仅过去5年，英国就有172个节日消失。 96 项赛事因新冠疫情而丢失，2023 年全年丢失了 36 项赛事，而现在，自年初以来已经丢失了 40 项赛事。</p><p>新数据由英国领先的非营利性音乐节贸易协会独立音乐节协会 (AIF) 分享，该协会代表 202 个英国音乐节的利益，容量从 500 到 80,000 人不等。</p><p> AIF 警告说，如果没有政府援助，这一趋势将继续增长，并透露，如果不进行干预，该国将在 2024 年看到 100 多个节日消失。</p><p>它凸显了当前的主要问题是不可预测的成本上升，而且自大流行以来，英国还没有一个稳定的节日季节来帮助其复苏——这意味着节日面临着比以往任何时候都更大的财务压力。</p><p> AIF 发布这份报告之前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/uk-festivals-cancelled-postponed-2023-2024-money-covid-weather-3577792">， <em>NME</em>调查了近年来为何如此多的英国音乐节被取消或推迟</a>，并与行业专家进行了交谈，揭示了音乐节的迅速衰落。</p><p>它强调了赫里福德郡的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nozstock-festival-to-end-after-26-years-due-to-cost-of-living-crisis-3554538">Nozstock Hidden Valley 如何因“成本飙升”和财务风险而宣布 26 年后的 2024 年将是他们的最后一次</a>，而 Shepton Mallet 滑冰和音乐节<a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-somerset-67286166">NASS 宣布他们不会在今年夏天举办活动</a>要么是因为“继续下去在经济上不可行”。</p><p>其他提到的还有被<a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/articles/c6p9455j0r4o">取消的邓弗里斯杜恩海姆音乐节（Dumfries&#39; Doonhame Festival）</a> 、蓝点音乐节（Bluedot）——去年夏天<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bluedot-festival-cancel-sunday-day-tickets-due-to-bad-weather-3472136">遭受大雨袭击和取消</a>后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bluedot-festival-to-take-fallow-year-in-2024-to-recover-after-rain-soaked-edition-3508624">，宣布放假一年，</a>让土地“拼命”恢复； <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nottinghams-splendour-festival-cancelled-leaving-organisers-frustrated-3576355">诺丁汉辉煌音乐节（Nottingham&#39;s Splendour）今年因计划延误而被取消。</a>财政困难的市议会和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/barn-on-the-farm-festival-postponed-until-2025-due-to-financial-difficulties-3576964">农场谷仓表示，由于财政限制，它将休耕一年</a>。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C58nf8Bqe_9/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022