绿日乐队以《Dookie》、《American Idiot》、热门歌曲和史诗般的舞台表演拉开了“Saviors”世界巡演的序幕https://www.nme.com/news/music/green-day-kick-off-saviors-world-tour-with-dookie-american-idiot-the-hits-and-epic-stage-show-3761403？ utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=green-day-kick-off-saviors-world-tour-with-dookie-american-idiot-the-hits-and-epic-stage-showAnagricel Duran Fri, 31 May 2024 17:14:02 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop-PunkRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3761403 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Green-Day-Performing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="绿日乐队 (Green Day) 的比利·乔·阿姆斯特朗 (Billie Joe Armstrong) 在加利福尼亚州洛杉矶杜比剧院举行的 2024 年 iHeartRadio 音乐奖颁奖典礼上登台表演。 （凯文·马祖尔/盖蒂图片社为 iHeartRadio 拍摄）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Green-Day-Performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Green-Day-Performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Green-Day-Performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Green-Day-Performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Green-Day-Performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Green-Day-Performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>该演出在西班牙戈佐山 O Son do Camino 音乐节上举行</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/green-day-kick-off-saviors-world-tour-with-dookie-american-idiot-the-hits-and-epic-stage-show-3761403">绿日乐队之后，以《Dookie》、《American Idiot》拉开了“Saviors”世界巡演的序幕，热门歌曲和史诗般的舞台表演</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Green-Day-Performing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="绿日乐队 (Green Day) 的比利·乔·阿姆斯特朗 (Billie Joe Armstrong) 在加利福尼亚州洛杉矶杜比剧院举行的 2024 年 iHeartRadio 音乐奖颁奖典礼上登台表演。 （凯文·马祖尔/盖蒂图片社为 iHeartRadio 拍摄）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Green-Day-Performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Green-Day-Performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Green-Day-Performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Green-Day-Performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Green-Day-Performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Green-Day-Performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/Green-Day">Green Day</a>昨晚（5 月 30 日）在西班牙拉开了他们大规模的“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/green-day-announce-2024-saviors-stadium-tour-including-huge-london-show-buy-tickets-3529041">Saviors</a> ”世界巡演的序幕，他们在那里演奏了一系列曲目。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/green-day-saviors-album-review-3567737"><b>绿日乐队 - 《救世主》评论：自《美国白痴》以来他们最好的作品</b></a></strong></li></ul><p>该乐队由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-joe-armstrong">Billie Joe Armstrong</a> 、Mike Dirnt 和 Tre Cool 组成，他们在西班牙戈佐山举行的 O Son do Camino 音乐节上登上了舞台，开始了巡演的第一晚。</p><p>他们以第 14 张录音室专辑《Saviors》中的主打单曲《The American Dream Is Killing Me》开场，然后进入他们 1994 年的 LP《Dookie》，完整播放了这首歌曲。阿姆斯特朗等人然后，他们以《Know Your Enemy》、《Dilemma》和《Brain Stew》作为短暂的中场休息，然后再完整地播放他们 2004 年的专辑《American Idiot》。</p><p> Green Day 的舞台布置包括一只巨大的手拿着一颗红色的手榴弹心，正如《American Idiot》的专辑插图中所见，舞台上堆放着许多 Marshall 扩音器。两张唱片——分别是“Dookie”和“American Idiot”——今年都庆祝了他们的 30 周年和 20 周年纪念日。乐队此前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/green-day-confirm-theyll-be-playing-dookie-and-american-idiot-in-full-on-2024-saviors-world-tour-3572429">承诺，他们将在巡演时完整播放两张专辑</a>。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="绿色日 - 九月结束时叫醒我 @ O Son do Camiño 2024" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/bXZrF4-J1KU?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" 